{"type":"custom_message","customType":"openclaw.runtime-context","content":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"user:ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b6f11b3a690a0b4ac6bf33730c95\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-05-12 07:01 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\"\n}\n```","display":false,"details":{"source":"openclaw-runtime-context"},"id":"30b30889","parentId":"9c91a193","timestamp":"2026-05-11T23:01:46.607Z"}
{"type":"message","id":"639608f7","parentId":"30b30889","timestamp":"2026-05-11T23:02:21.147Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"HALEI 说没钱买 token 了，想让我设计一个 agent 帮他网上赚钱。\n\n这是一个比较敏感的话题。用户想通过\"agent 网上赚钱\"，但没有任何具体计划或方向。\n\n我需要非常谨慎。网上赚钱这个需求很宽泛，可能涉及到：\n1. 正当途径：内容创作、社群运营、电商、直播带货、知识付费等\n2. 不正当途径：诈骗、传销、灰产等\n\n我不能参与任何灰产、诈骗或疑似欺诈的计划。我需要了解用户的具体情况、能力边界、风险偏好，再给出合理的建议。\n\n但首先，我需要了解用户的基本情况：\n- 时间充裕度（用户说晚上可用来学习探索）\n- 具体技能或资源\n- 能投入的启动资金\n- 风险承受能力\n \n我先问清楚用户的具体能力和资源优势，这样我可以给出更切合实际的建议。用户现在的表达很模糊，我需要更多的上下文才能给出可行的方案。\n\n我会采取直接但谨慎的方式，逐步了解用户的详细情况。\n","thinkingSignature":"59af3a6f3a84a5ebee3a81c6d0e9400f1f40706a7572e43c00e08e1d45a1d945"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n理解你的紧迫感。但\"网上赚钱\"太宽泛了——我不知道你的能力边界、启动资金和风险偏好，直接给计划是在浪费你的时间。\n\n先跟我说几个事，我好帮你定向：\n\n1. **你能投入什么？**\n   - 时间（每天几小时？）\n   - 启动资金（有，还是零？）\n   - 已有资源（粉丝、账号、技能、硬件设备）\n\n2. **你对哪种方式相对感兴趣？**\n   - 出内容的（短视频、图文、直播）\n   - 卖东西的（电商、代购、知识付费）\n   - 卖劳力的（外包、众包、在线任务）\n   - 其他\n\n3. **你讨厌什么？**\n   - 不想出镜？\n   - 不想垫钱？\n   - 排斥拉人头？\n\n给个大概方向，我帮你拆解一个最小可行的路径——先跑通再说，不画大饼。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":24214,"output":382,"cacheRead":320,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":24916,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778540506607,"responseId":"065192dd298cf523385cd864ba663d83"}}
{"type":"message","id":"0ed9aefd","parentId":"639608f7","timestamp":"2026-05-11T23:02:59.418Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[message_id: om_x100b6f124ccacca0c34942cb8637d3e]\nou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb: 从我的角度来说，我是不愿意出镜的"}],"timestamp":1778540579403}}
{"type":"custom_message","customType":"openclaw.runtime-context","content":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"user:ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b6f124ccacca0c34942cb8637d3e\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-05-12 07:02 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\"\n}\n```","display":false,"details":{"source":"openclaw-runtime-context"},"id":"2e8e3321","parentId":"0ed9aefd","timestamp":"2026-05-11T23:02:59.419Z"}
{"type":"message","id":"15a7188a","parentId":"2e8e3321","timestamp":"2026-05-11T23:03:15.792Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user doesn't want to appear on camera. Let me think about viable options that don't require appearing on camera.\n\nOptions for making money online without appearing on camera:\n1. 无人直播 (AI数字人/图文循环)\n2. 内容代写/搬运\n3. 跨境电商 (TikTok Shop等) - without showing face\n4. 信息差套利\n5. 撸平台羊毛 (任务平台)\n6. 知识付费 (图文)\n7. AI工具服务\n\nLet me ask more questions to narrow down the direction.\n","thinkingSignature":"4d893fa8dd57966b09911fa700481765b2779168f819ff2c05c070f6dba5dc1e"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n不出镜筛掉了短视频、直播这两个最常见的赛道，但还有不少路可以走。\n\n再问两件事：\n\n1. **你愿意用 AI 数字人/虚拟形象代替出镜吗？**\n   - 有些平台支持AI克隆或虚拟主播，可以不露脸\n\n2. **你愿意卖虚拟的东西还是实物？**\n   - 虚拟（教程、素材、软件、服务）→ 成本低，边际成本为零\n   - 实物（带货、开店）→ 需要垫钱/压货，门槛高一点\n\n---\n\n结合你\"不愿意出镜\"和\"快买不起 token\"的现状，我觉得**最现实的起点**可能是：\n\n> **先跑通一个\"信息差变现\"的小闭环——用 AI 工具帮别人做内容或解决痛点，收到钱再说。**\n\n比如：\n- 帮人做图文（小红书、公众号）\n- 帮人做设计/视频素材\n- 撸平台任务（有平台会撒钱拉新）\n\n你倾向哪个方向？我帮你拆具体步骤。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":24458,"output":324,"cacheRead":320,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":25102,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778540579419,"responseId":"0651932470bbaf99884e57a029fedc1a"}}
{"type":"message","id":"78d1e25c","parentId":"15a7188a","timestamp":"2026-05-11T23:03:32.773Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[message_id: om_x100b6f124ae928b0c3b580879f1b00f]\nou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb: 不是，我是让你设计一个agent，赚钱的，在网上。你怎么让我去赚钱呀？"}],"timestamp":1778540612755}}
{"type":"custom_message","customType":"openclaw.runtime-context","content":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"user:ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b6f124ae928b0c3b580879f1b00f\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-05-12 07:03 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\"\n}\n```","display":false,"details":{"source":"openclaw-runtime-context"},"id":"bacfcdee","parentId":"78d1e25c","timestamp":"2026-05-11T23:03:32.774Z"}
{"type":"message","id":"9858870c","parentId":"bacfcdee","timestamp":"2026-05-11T23:04:10.469Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"ah, I see! The user wants me to design an AI agent that can make money online, not help the user personally go and make money. They want to create an autonomous agent that operates on the internet to generate income.\n\nThis is actually a very interesting request. They want me to architect an AI agent that:\n1. Operates autonomously on the internet\n2. Earns money without the user actively working\n3. Ideally runs 24/7\n\nThis is a system design task - I need to think about what kind of agent would be viable. Let me think about real approaches:\n\n1. **Content creation agent** - creates and publishes content (blogs, social media posts, YouTube descriptions, etc.) and monetizes through ads/affiliates\n\n\n2. **E-commerce agent** - manages stores, does product research, runs listings\n3. **Affiliate marketing agent** - finds opportunities, creates content, drives traffic\n4. **Data gathering/reselling** - collects and sells information\n5. **Automation service agent** - sells AI automation services to businesses\n\nThe real question is what actually works given current technology constraints. An agent that fully operates autonomously with its own payment infrastructure is complex, so I should focus on something more practical - like an agent that identifies and exploits information gaps across platforms, creates content automatically, and monetizes through affiliate links or ad revenue.\n\nBut I need to be careful here about what's actually viable. Content publishing typically requires user authentication, payment processing needs identity verification, and most platforms have friction that prevents truly autonomous operation. The more realistic approaches are things like publishing to platforms that already have monetization built in, creating content that generates affiliate revenue, or providing services that can be delivered automatically.\n\nA content curation and publishing agent seems like the strongest starting point - it can find trending topics, generate content around them, publish to platforms that support creator monetization, and track performance to optimize. This avoids the need for the agent to handle payments directly while still generating income.\n\nFor the actual architecture, I'm thinking about how to split responsibilities: one agent handles research and discovers what's trending, another generates content, and a third publishes and monitors. They share context so each step informs the next. The workflow would be gathering signals from trending topics, creating something worth publishing, posting it to platforms, and then monitoring how it performs. But the real bottleneck is that platforms need real user accounts and authentication, which is a constraint I can't get around with just software.\n\nI should be straightforward with the user about what's actually possible versus what would need manual setup, and focus on what I can actually design and implement.\n","thinkingSignature":"0b6da40461f7f05c8c58ca722f04ce10822646a55b039d0d05fa542e5a4f136a"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n明白了！你要的是**一个能自己运转、自动生成收入的 AI Agent 系统**，不是让你自己去干活。\n\n我来帮你设计这个系统。\n\n---\n\n## 🎯 赚钱 Agent 架构设计\n\n### 核心思路\n**信息差套利**：让 Agent 自动发现互联网上的套利机会（流量红利、平台补贴、差价格差），持续运转并变现。\n\n### 模块划分\n\n| 模块 | 职责 | 技术方案 |\n|------|------|----------|\n| 🔍 情报员 | 监控平台补贴、流量红利、热门话题、价格差 | SearXNG + 平台 API |\n| ✍️ 内容员 | 批量生成内容（图文/短视频脚本/测评） | LLM + 多模态 |\n| 📡 发布员 | 自动发布到平台 + 管理账号 | 各平台官方 API / Browser 自动化 |\n| 💰 变现阶段 | 接入广告、带货、Affiliate 链接 | 平台创作者计划 + 第三方联盟 |\n| 📊 审计员 | 追踪哪个内容赚钱，持续优化 | 数据分析 + A/B 测试 |\n\n### 工作流\n\n```\n情报员发现机会 \n  → 内容员生成内容 \n    → 发布员自动发布 \n      → 变现阶段接入收入 \n        → 审计员反馈优化\n```\n\n### 变现路径优先级\n\n1. **平台补贴**：今日头条、百家号、公众号 → 按阅读量补贴\n2. **Affiliate**：推广带货链接，卖出抽佣\n3. **广告接单**：小红书/公众号接品牌广告\n4. **信息差倒卖**：发现低价资源，高价转售\n\n### 最大瓶颈\n\nAgent 自己没法注册账号、实名认证、绑定收款——这部分**必须你本人实名注册**。Agent 只负责运营。\n\n---\n\n你先把你的飞书账号、常用平台账号（头条/小红书/公众号等）告诉我，我帮你设计具体的**部署方案和启动步骤**。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":551,"output":925,"cacheRead":24512,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":25988,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778540612774,"responseId":"065193450ec0c2c79411cdd3b841a1d0"}}
